Steps to creat a new database in Pgadmin4:
connect your server (PostSQL11)
click on the Database and selet create Database
in the pop up type the name of Database and select postgres as a owner and save the changes
At this point you need you need to add the Extention
Click on the Extention and select create Extention.In the pop up windowe select postgis for name drop down list
To create Schemas citydb_pkg follow the step below:
open the text file CONNECTION_DETAIL.SH through directory type cd /Applications/3DCityDB-Importer-Exporter/3dcitydb/postgresql/ShellScripts/Unix/
opent the terminal 
type cd /Applications/3DCityDB-Importer-Exporter/3dcitydb/postgresql/ShellScripts/Unix/
type chmod u+x CREATE_DB.sh
type ./CREATE_DB.sh
type the code 25833
enter
type urn:ogc:def:crs,crs:EPSG:6.12:25833,crs:EPSG:6.12:5783
Refresh your Database 
